{"tid":2478582,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"EQS","createTime":"2021-04-07T07:19:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T07:19:53.000Z","uid":296589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e15232afee14aa8dd2b98f5488b2c1a16c948c23","tid":2478582,"uid":296589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T07:19:53.000Z","msg":"根據賓士公告，他們即將在今年發表的電動車旗艦 EQS，將擁有超過 700 公里的續航力，而且是採用歐盟 WLTP 標準。<br />\n<br />\nEQS 配有 108kWh 電池組，而 WLTP 成績高達 770 公里，代表能源效率來到 140Wh/km。作為比較，特斯拉 Model S 的 WLTP 成績是 593 公里，能源效率為 193Wh/km。<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSh6GVAQ74SxgQqw36BfietUr7S7gBw5E2gawPqBsuKFY?filename=cPZQiuu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcPZQiuu.jpg&h=b082af06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2021/04/01/benz-range-anxiety-is-gone-eqs-700km/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2021%2F04%2F01%2Fbenz-range-anxiety-is-gone-eqs-700km%2F&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtG58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=f700af74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2021/04/01/benz-range-anxiety-is-gone-eqs-700km/</a>"}]}